cast.overview: The story of Gary Valentine and Alana Kane growing up, running around and going through the treacherous navigation of first love in the San Fernando Valley, 1973.
cast.title: Licorice Pizza

details.biography: James Kelley is an American actor best known for playing the role of Danny Cahill in Creedmoria and Louie in Squall. He was born and raised in Connecticut alongside his two brothers. He attended Wilton High School. His first role was opposite Aunjanue Ellis and Ebon Moss-Bachrach in the film The Volunteer, filmed in Connecticut.
details.name: James Kelley
